# ===========================================================================
# ADV-EAC-04 — trigger_hit_animation() called before first _physics_process tick.
#
# VULNERABILITY: Primary suite always primes the controller with one tick before
# calling trigger_hit_animation(). Calling it before any tick means _current_clip
# is still "" (initial value per AC-5.6). The hit path must not crash even when
